testtool.models.grader

Class ReleaseOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • testtool.models.grader.ReleaseOptions

  • public class ReleaseOptions
extends java.lang.Object
    The ReleaseOptions class is meant to be a dialogue to allow the Instructor or Proctor to decide what sorts of options to release a graded test with. Options could include: Just show grade, only show missed questions, show all questions, etc.
    Version:
    14apr14
    Author:
    RJ Almada (rjalmada@calpoly.edu)
